## Attribution requirement

Per Section 3(a), attribution of this work MUST include:

- The present work's citation (see CITATION.cff).
- Gagne's prior Sentinel framework as the primary dependency (see
  ATTRIBUTION.md).

Citing only the present work without citing Gagne is a violation of the
attribution-discipline norm this repository is published under, even if
it meets the bare letter of CC-BY-4.0 attribution requirements for this
work alone.

## What this license does not cover

- The drift-engine implementation is not licensed under CC-BY-4.0 and is
  not included in this repository.
- Gagne's corpus and rig are licensed under their own license (see
  ATTRIBUTION.md and references/gagne-sentinel.md); our use of them is
  governed by that license, not this one.
